WEBVTT

00:00.692 --> 00:03.743
Football is the greatest drama on Earth.

00:05.329 --> 00:06.716
This is our stage.

00:07.475 --> 00:08.281
Our theater.

00:10.254 --> 00:11.425
I was born into it.

00:12.952 --> 00:14.582
Others were adopted.

00:15.959 --> 00:17.503
But we're all connected.

00:18.842 --> 00:22.460
If you don't believe we're family, you haven't felt what we felt:...

00:23.738 --> 00:28.738
...agony, tension, heartbreak.

00:29.946 --> 00:36.789
But that moment, when it comes together just right, words cannot describe it.

00:39.539 --> 00:45.064
An entire season changes with one kick, one bad decision, one slip.

00:47.312 --> 00:51.819
But one magic moment lives in our hearts forever.

00:56.911 --> 00:59.339
This is football.

01:10.121 --> 01:11.336
FIFA 15.

01:13.897 --> 01:14.729
Feel the game.

